column5: Anyone know how the ice is doing at Virginia Beach? Ice out that is.  Thanks, LTF
I saw something on FB showing open water as far as you could see today.  S.
Thanks Sinker! I guess the time is near
It could be full of ice again now so be prepared. I havent been out.  S.

Folks fishing this area this season should be aware that many small Musky came through the ice ( and back down) this past season, a good sign that the stocking is doing well. If more are caught, please remember to let them go and handle with care...
